791633,149,25,2,5,1,23,2,Chandajātassa {jantuno}ti. 
791634,149,25,6,32,1,228,24,"{Chando}ti yo kāmesu kāmacchando kāmarāgo kāmanandī kāmataṇhā kāmasneho kāmapariḷāho kāmamucchā kāmajjhosānaṃ kāmogho kāmayogo kāmupādānaṃ kāmacchandanīvaraṇaṃ, tassa so kāmacchando jāto hoti sañjāto nibbatto abhinibbatto pātubhūto. "
791635,149,25,33,48,1,124,13,{Jantuno}ti sattassa narassa mānavassa posassa puggalassa jīvassa jāgussa jantussa indagussa manujassāti– chandajātassa jantuno. 
791636,149,26,2,18,1,68,11,"Te kāmā {parihāyantī}ti– te vā kāmā parihāyanti, so vā kāmehi parihāyati. "
791637,149,26,19,23,1,26,4,Kathaṃ te kāmā parihāyanti? 
791638,149,26,24,80,1,270,39,"Tassa tiṭṭhantasseva te bhoge rājāno vā haranti, corā vā haranti, aggi vā dahati, udakaṃ vā vahati, appiyā vā dāyādā haranti, nihitaṃ vā nādhigacchati, duppayuttā vā kammantā bhijjanti, kule vā kulaṅgāro uppajjati, yo te bhoge vikirati vidhamati[ vidhameti( syā.)] viddhaṃseti aniccatāyeva aṭṭhamī. "
791639,149,26,81,90,1,87,9,Evaṃ te kāmā hāyanti parihāyanti paridhaṃsenti paripatanti antaradhāyanti vippalujjanti. 
791640,149,26,91,95,1,27,4,Kathaṃ so kāmehi parihāyati? 
791641,149,26,96,103,1,50,7,Tiṭṭhanteva te bhoge so cavati marati vippalujjati. 
791642,149,26,104,113,1,83,9,Evaṃ so kāmehi hāyati parihāyati paridhaṃseti paripatati antaradhāyati vippalujjati. 
791643,149,27,2,9,1,39,6,"Corā haranti rājāno, aggi dahati nassati; "
791644,149,28,2,24,1,39,5,"Atha antena jahati[ atho antena heti( syā.), asahantena dahati( ka.)], sarīraṃ sapariggahaṃ; "
791645,149,29,2,9,1,42,6,"Etadaññāya medhāvī, bhuñjetha ca dadetha ca. "
791646,149,30,2,15,1,82,11,"Datvā ca bhutvā ca yathānubhāvaṃ, anindito saggamupeti ṭhānanti, te kāmā parihāyanti. "
791647,149,31,2,5,1,23,2,Sallaviddhova {ruppatī}ti. 
791648,149,31,6,40,1,285,30,"Yathā ayomayena vā sallena viddho, aṭṭhimayena vā sallena dantamayena vā sallena visāṇamayena vā sallena kaṭṭhamayena vā sallena viddho ruppati kuppati ghaṭṭīyati pīḷīyati, byādhito domanassito hoti, evameva vatthukāmānaṃ vipariṇāmaññathābhāvā uppajjanti sokaparidevadukkhadomanassupāyāsā. "
791649,149,31,41,58,1,125,15,"So kāmasallena ca sokasallena ca viddho, ruppati kuppati ghaṭṭīyati pīḷīyati byādhito domanassito hotīti– sallaviddhova ruppati. "
