791730,149,61,13,30,1,114,11,"{Bandhū}ti cattāro bandhū– ñātibandhavāpi bandhu, gottabandhavāpi bandhu, mantabandhavāpi bandhu, sippabandhavāpi bandhu. "
791731,149,61,31,36,1,22,4,Puthu {kāme}ti bahū kāme. 
791732,149,61,37,52,1,77,12,Ete puthu kāmā manāpikā rūpā… pe… manāpikā phoṭṭhabbāti– thiyo bandhū puthu kāme. 
791733,149,62,2,6,1,21,3,Yo naro {anugijjhatī}ti. 
791734,149,62,7,34,1,172,24,{Yo}ti yo yādiso yathāyutto yathāvihito yathāpakāro yaṃṭhānappatto yaṃdhammasamannāgato khattiyo vā brāhmaṇo vā vesso vā suddo vā gahaṭṭho vā pabbajito pvā devo vā manusso vā. 
791735,149,62,35,47,1,67,11,{Naro}ti satto naro mānavo poso puggalo jīvo jāgu jantu indagu manujo. 
791736,149,62,48,60,1,108,10,{Anugijjhatī}ti kilesakāmena vatthukāmesu gijjhati anugijjhati paligijjhati palibajjhatīti– yo naro anugijjhati. 
