791824,149,108,2,7,1,23,4,Tasmā jantu sadā {sato}ti. 
791825,149,108,8,21,1,94,11,{Tasmā}ti tasmā taṃkāraṇā taṃhetu tappaccayā taṃnidānā etaṃ ādīnavaṃ sampassamāno kāmesūti– tasmā. 
791826,149,108,22,34,1,68,11,{Jantū}ti satto naro mānavo poso puggalo jīvo jāgu jantu indagu manujo. 
791827,149,108,35,80,1,300,31,"{Sadā}ti sadā sabbadā sabbakālaṃ niccakālaṃ dhuvakālaṃ satataṃ samitaṃ abbokiṇṇaṃ poṅkhānupoṅkhaṃ udakūmikajātaṃ avīci santati sahitaṃ phassitaṃ[ phusitaṃ( sī. syā.)], purebhattaṃ pacchābhattaṃ purimayāmaṃ majjhimayāmaṃ pacchimayāmaṃ, kāḷe juṇhe vasse hemante gimhe, purime vayokhandhe majjhime vayokhandhe pacchime vayokhandhe. "
791828,149,108,81,100,1,140,14,"{Sato}ti catūhi kāraṇehi sato– kāye kāyānupassanāsatipaṭṭhānaṃ bhāvento sato, vedanāsu… citte… dhammesu dhammānupassanāsatipaṭṭhānaṃ bhāvento sato. "
