791832,149,109,30,42,1,87,10,Kāmāni {parivajjaye}ti dvīhi kāraṇehi kāme parivajjeyya– vikkhambhanato vā samucchedato vā. 
791833,149,109,43,47,1,39,4,Kathaṃ vikkhambhanato kāme parivajjeyya?
791834,149,109,48,94,1,322,30,"‘‘ Aṭṭhikaṅkalūpamā kāmā appassādaṭṭhenā’’ ti passanto vikkhambhanato kāme parivajjeyya,‘‘ maṃsapesūpamā kāmā bahusādhāraṇaṭṭhenā’’ ti passanto vikkhambhanato kāme parivajjeyya,‘‘ tiṇukkūpamā kāmā anudahanaṭṭhenā’’ ti passanto vikkhambhanato kāme parivajjeyya… pe… nevasaññānāsaññāyatanasamāpattiṃ bhāvento vikkhambhanato kāme parivajjeyya. "
