792418,149,314,224,229,1,38,4,Evampi– sakañhi diṭṭhiṃ kathamaccayeyya. 
792419,149,315,2,6,1,30,3,Chandānunīto ruciyā {niviṭṭho}ti. 
792420,149,315,7,21,1,111,13,{Chandānunīto}ti sakāya diṭṭhiyā sakāya khantiyā sakāya ruciyā sakāya laddhiyā yāyati niyyati vuyhati saṃharīyati. 
792421,149,315,22,60,1,275,35,"Yathā hatthiyānena vā assayānena vā rathayānena vā goyānena vā ajayānena vā meṇḍayānena vā oṭṭhayānena vā kharayānena vā yāyati niyyati vuyhati saṃharīyati, evameva sakāya diṭṭhiyā sakāya khantiyā sakāya ruciyā sakāya laddhiyā yāyati niyyati vuyhati saṃharīyatīti– chandānunīto. "
792422,149,315,61,81,1,149,17,Ruciyā {niviṭṭho}ti sakāya diṭṭhiyā sakāya ruciyā sakāya laddhiyā niviṭṭho patiṭṭhito allīno upagato ajjhosito adhimuttoti – chandānunīto ruciyā niviṭṭho. 
