793510,149,726,13,30,1,89,14,"Dhono diṭṭhaṃ na maññati, diṭṭhasmiṃ na maññati, diṭṭhato na maññati, diṭṭhā meti na maññati; "
793511,149,726,31,47,1,76,13,"sutaṃ na maññati, sutasmiṃ na maññati, sutato na maññati, sutaṃ meti na maññati; "
793512,149,726,48,64,1,76,13,"mutaṃ na maññati, mutasmiṃ na maññati, mutato na maññati, mutaṃ meti na maññati; "
793513,149,726,65,81,1,88,13,"viññātaṃ na maññati, viññātasmiṃ na maññati, viññātato na maññati, viññātaṃ meti na maññati. "
793514,149,726,82,85,1,24,3,Vuttampi hetaṃ bhagavatā–
793515,149,726,86,125,1,276,25,"‘‘ asmīti, bhikkhave, maññitametaṃ, ayamahamasmīti maññitametaṃ, bhavissanti maññitametaṃ, na bhavissanti maññitametaṃ, rūpī bhavissanti maññitametaṃ, arūpī bhavissanti maññitametaṃ, saññī bhavissanti maññitametaṃ, asaññī bhavissanti maññitametaṃ, nevasaññīnāsaññī bhavissanti maññitametaṃ. "
793516,149,726,126,148,1,72,9,"Maññitaṃ[ maññitaṃ hi( sī.)], bhikkhave, rogo, maññitaṃ gaṇḍo, maññitaṃ sallaṃ, maññitaṃ upaddavo. "
793517,149,726,149,175,1,142,18,"Tasmātiha, bhikkhave, amaññamānena cetasā viharissāmāti, evañhi vo, bhikkhave, sikkhitabban’’ ti– dhono na hi tena maññati yadidaṃ diṭṭhasutamutesu vā. "
793518,149,727,2,6,1,26,2,Nāññena {visuddhimicchatī}ti. 
793519,149,727,7,46,1,355,38,Dhono aññena asuddhimaggena micchāpaṭipadāya aniyyānikapathena aññatra satipaṭṭhānehi aññatra sammappadhānehi aññatra iddhipādehi aññatra indriyehi aññatra balehi aññatra bojjhaṅgehi aññatra ariyā aṭṭhaṅgikā maggā suddhiṃ visuddhiṃ parisuddhiṃ muttiṃ vimuttiṃ parimuttiṃ na icchati na sādiyati na pattheti na piheti nābhijappatīti– nāññena visuddhimicchati. 
793520,149,728,2,9,1,31,6,Na hi so rajjati no {virajjatī}ti. 
793521,149,728,10,19,1,82,8,"Sabbe bālaputhujjanā rajjanti, puthujjanakalyāṇakaṃ upādāya satta sekkhā virajjanti; "
793522,149,728,20,25,1,31,5,arahā neva rajjati no virajjati. 
793523,149,728,26,39,1,88,11,"Viratto so khayā rāgassa vītarāgattā, khayā dosassa vītadosattā, khayā mohassa vītamohattā. "
793524,149,728,40,58,1,106,14,"So vuṭṭhavāso ciṇṇacaraṇo… pe… jātijarāmaraṇasaṃsāro, natthi tassa punabbhavoti– na hi so rajjati no virajjati. "
793525,149,729,2,5,1,14,2,Tenāha bhagavā–
793526,149,730,2,14,1,52,9,"‘ ‘ Dhono na hi tena maññati, yadidaṃ diṭṭhasutamutesu vā; "
793527,149,731,2,14,1,57,9,"Nāññena visuddhimicchati, na hi so rajjati no virajjatī’’ ti. "
793528,149,732,2,4,1,24,2,Jarāsuttaniddeso chaṭṭho. 
