793532,149,736,2,10,1,19,1,"Methunamanuyuttassa ,[ iccāyasmā tisso metteyyo] "
793533,149,737,2,5,1,21,3,Vighātaṃ brūhi mārisa; 
793534,149,738,2,8,1,41,5,"Sutvāna tava sāsanaṃ, viveke sikkhissāmase. "
793535,149,739,2,4,1,21,1,{Methunamanuyuttassā}ti . 
793536,149,739,5,16,1,109,11,Methunadhammo nāma yo so asaddhammo gāmadhammo vasaladhammo duṭṭhullo odakantiko rahasso dvayaṃdvayasamāpatti. 
793537,149,739,17,20,1,31,3,Kiṃkāraṇā vuccati methunadhammo? 
793538,149,739,21,34,1,136,12,Ubhinnaṃ rattānaṃ sārattānaṃ avassutānaṃ pariyuṭṭhitānaṃ pariyādinnacittānaṃ ubhinnaṃ sadisānaṃ dhammoti– taṃkāraṇā vuccati methunadhammo. 
793539,149,739,35,71,1,275,29,"Yathā ubho kalahakārakā methunakāti vuccanti, ubho bhaṇḍanakārakā methunakāti vuccanti, ubho bhassakārakā methunakāti vuccanti, ubho vivādakārakā methunakāti vuccanti, ubho adhikaraṇakārakā methunakāti vuccanti, ubho vādino methunakāti vuccanti, ubho sallāpakā methunakāti vuccanti; "
793540,149,739,72,86,1,145,13,evamevaṃ ubhinnaṃ rattānaṃ sārattānaṃ avassutānaṃ pariyuṭṭhitānaṃ pariyādinnacittānaṃ ubhinnaṃ sadisānaṃ dhammoti– taṃkāraṇā vuccati methunadhammo. 
793541,149,740,2,4,1,21,1,{Methunamanuyuttassā}ti . 
793542,149,740,5,21,1,189,14,Methunadhamme yuttassa payuttassa āyuttassa samāyuttassa taccaritassa tabbahulassa taggarukassa tanninnassa tappoṇassa tappabbhārassa tadadhimuttassa tadadhipateyyassāti – methunamanuyuttassa. 
793543,149,741,2,6,1,26,3,Iccāyasmā tisso {metteyyo}ti. 
793544,149,741,7,18,1,104,8,{Iccā}ti padasandhi padasaṃsaggo padapāripūrī akkharasamavāyo byañjanasiliṭṭhatā padānupubbatāpetaṃ– iccāti. 
793545,149,741,19,27,1,79,6,{Āyasmā}ti piyavacanaṃ garuvacanaṃ sagāravavacanaṃ sappatissavacanametaṃ– āyasmāti. 
793546,149,741,28,43,1,115,14,{Tisso}ti tassa therassa nāmaṃ saṅkhā samaññā paññatti vohāro nāmaṃ nāmakammaṃ nāmadheyyaṃ nirutti byañjanaṃ abhilāpo. 
793547,149,741,44,58,1,90,11,{Metteyyo}ti tassa therassa gottaṃ saṅkhā samaññā paññatti vohāroti– iccāyasmā tisso metteyyo. 
793548,149,742,2,6,1,23,3,Vighātaṃ brūhi {mārisā}ti. 
793549,149,742,7,32,1,147,17,Vighātan ti vighātaṃ upaghātaṃ pīḷanaṃ ghaṭṭanaṃ upaddavaṃ upasaggaṃ brūhi ācikkha desehi paññapehi paṭṭhapehi vivara vibhaja uttānīkarohi[ uttāniṃ karohi( ka.)] pakāsehi. 
793550,149,742,33,44,1,101,9,{Mārisā}ti piyavacanaṃ garuvacanaṃ sagāravavacanaṃ sappatissavacanametaṃ mārisāti– vighātaṃ brūhi mārisa. 
793551,149,743,2,6,1,23,4,Sutvāna tava sāsanan ti. 
793552,149,743,7,22,1,131,14,Tuyhaṃ vacanaṃ byappathaṃ desanaṃ anusāsanaṃ anusiṭṭhiṃ sutvā suṇitvā uggahetvā upadhārayitvā upalakkhayitvāti– sutvāna tava sāsanaṃ. 
793553,149,744,2,5,1,22,2,Viveke {sikkhissāmase}ti. 
793554,149,744,6,16,1,56,6,"{Viveko}ti tayo vivekā– kāyaviveko, cittaviveko, upadhiviveko. "
793555,149,744,17,19,1,17,2,Katamo kāyaviveko? 
793556,149,744,20,39,1,155,17,"Idha bhikkhu vivittaṃ senāsanaṃ bhajati araññaṃ rukkhamūlaṃ pabbataṃ kandaraṃ giriguhaṃ susānaṃ vanapatthaṃ abbhokāsaṃ palāsapuñjaṃ , kāyena vivitto viharati. "
793557,149,744,40,84,1,222,33,"So eko gacchati, eko tiṭṭhati, eko nisīdati, eko seyyaṃ kappeti, eko gāmaṃ piṇḍāya pavisati, eko paṭikkamati, eko raho nisīdati , eko caṅkamaṃ adhiṭṭhāti, eko carati, eko viharati iriyati vattati pāleti yapeti yāpeti– ayaṃ kāyaviveko. "
793558,149,745,2,4,1,18,2,Katamo cittaviveko? 
793559,149,745,5,132,1,1173,112,"Paṭhamaṃ jhānaṃ samāpannassa nīvaraṇehi cittaṃ vivittaṃ hoti, dutiyaṃ jhānaṃ samāpannassa vitakkavicārehi cittaṃ vivittaṃ hoti, tatiyaṃ jhānaṃ samāpannassa pītiyā cittaṃ vivittaṃ hoti, catutthaṃ jhānaṃ samāpannassa sukhadukkhehi cittaṃ vivittaṃ hoti, ākāsānañcāyatanaṃ samāpannassa rūpasaññāya paṭighasaññāya nānattasaññāya cittaṃ vivittaṃ hoti, viññāṇañcāyatanaṃ samāpannassa ākāsānañcāyatanasaññāya cittaṃ vivittaṃ hoti, ākiñcaññāyatanaṃ samāpannassa viññāṇañcāyatanasaññāya cittaṃ vivittaṃ hoti, nevasaññānāsaññāyatanaṃ samāpannassa ākiñcaññāyatanasaññāya cittaṃ vivittaṃ hoti, sotāpannassa sakkāyadiṭṭhiyā vicikicchāya sīlabbataparāmāsā diṭṭhānusayā vicikicchānusayā tadekaṭṭhehi ca kilesehi cittaṃ vivittaṃ hoti, sakadāgāmissa oḷārikā kāmarāgasaññojanā paṭighasaññojanā oḷārikā kāmarāgānusayā paṭighānusayā tadekaṭṭhehi ca kilesehi cittaṃ vivittaṃ hoti, anāgāmissa anusahagatā kāmarāgasaññojanā paṭighasaññojanā anusahagatā kāmarāgānusayā paṭighānusayā tadekaṭṭhehi ca kilesehi cittaṃ vivittaṃ hoti, arahato rūparāgā arūparāgā mānā uddhaccā avijjāya mānānusayā bhavarāgānusayā avijjānusayā tadekaṭṭhehi ca kilesehi bahiddhā ca sabbanimittehi cittaṃ vivittaṃ hoti– ayaṃ cittaviveko. "
793560,149,746,2,4,1,19,2,Katamo upadhiviveko? 
793561,149,746,5,13,1,52,8,Upadhi vuccanti kilesā ca khandhā ca abhisaṅkhārā ca. 
793562,149,746,14,18,1,36,4,Upadhiviveko vuccati amataṃ nibbānaṃ. 
793563,149,746,19,30,1,103,10,Yo so sabbasaṅkhārasamatho sabbūpadhipaṭinissaggo taṇhakkhayo virāgo nirodho nibbānaṃ– ayaṃ upadhiviveko. 
793564,149,746,31,35,1,51,4,Kāyaviveko ca vivekaṭṭhakāyānaṃ nekkhammābhiratānaṃ; 
793565,149,746,36,40,1,54,4,cittaviveko ca parisuddhacittānaṃ paramavodānapattānaṃ; 
793566,149,746,41,46,1,57,5,upadhiviveko ca nirūpadhīnaṃ puggalānaṃ visaṅkhāragatānaṃ. 
793567,149,746,47,50,1,22,2,Viveke {sikkhissāmase}ti. 
793568,149,746,51,55,1,32,4,So thero pakatiyā sikkhitasikkho. 
793569,149,746,56,75,1,81,9,Api ca dhammadesanaṃ upādāya dhammadesanaṃ sāvento[ yācanto( sī. syā.)] evamāha– viveke sikkhissāmaseti. 
