793703,149,800,105,145,1,187,28,"‘‘ Bhātā me posetabbo… bhaginī me posetabbā… putto me posetabbo… dhītā me posetabbā… mittā me posetabbā… amaccā me posetabbā… ñātakā me posetabbā… sālohitā me posetabbā, tenamhi vibbhanto’’ ti bhaṇati. "
793704,149,800,146,160,1,112,12,"Vacīsatthaṃ karoti saṅkaroti janeti sañjaneti nibbatteti abhinibbattetīti– atha satthāni kurute, paravādehi codito. "
