793847,149,855,2,7,1,30,4,Idheva suddhiṃ iti {vādayantī}ti. 
793848,149,855,8,20,1,109,12,Idheva suddhiṃ visuddhiṃ parisuddhiṃ muttiṃ vimuttiṃ parimuttiṃ vadanti kathenti bhaṇanti dīpayanti voharanti.
793849,149,855,21,43,1,145,17,"‘‘ Sassato loko, idameva saccaṃ moghamaññan’’ ti suddhiṃ visuddhiṃ parisuddhiṃ muttiṃ vimuttiṃ parimuttiṃ vadanti kathenti bhaṇanti dīpayanti voharanti."
793850,149,855,44,117,1,396,58,"‘‘ Asassato loko … antavā loko… anantavā loko… taṃ jīvaṃ taṃ sarīraṃ… aññaṃ jīvaṃ aññaṃ sarīraṃ… hoti tathāgato paraṃ maraṇā… na hoti tathāgato paraṃ maraṇā… hoti ca na ca hoti tathāgato paraṃ maraṇā… neva hoti na na hoti tathāgato paraṃ maraṇā, idameva saccaṃ moghamaññan’’ ti suddhiṃ visuddhiṃ parisuddhiṃ muttiṃ vimuttiṃ parimuttiṃ vadanti kathenti bhaṇanti dīpayanti voharantīti– idheva suddhiṃ iti vādayanti. "
793851,149,856,2,6,1,31,3,Nāññesu dhammesu {visuddhimāhū}ti. 
793852,149,856,7,20,1,119,13,Attano satthāraṃ dhammakkhānaṃ gaṇaṃ diṭṭhiṃ paṭipadaṃ maggaṃ ṭhapetvā sabbe paravāde khipanti ukkhipanti parikkhipanti.
793853,149,856,21,104,1,459,67,"‘‘ So satthā na sabbaññū, dhammo na svākkhāto , gaṇo na suppaṭipanno, diṭṭhi na bhaddikā, paṭipadā na supaññattā , maggo na niyyāniko, natthettha suddhi vā visuddhi vā parisuddhi vā mutti vā vimutti vā parimutti vā, na tattha sujjhanti vā visujjhanti vā parisujjhanti vā muccanti vā vimuccanti vā parimuccanti vā, hīnā nihīnā omakā lāmakā chatukkā parittā’’ ti– evamāhaṃsu evaṃ vadanti evaṃ kathenti evaṃ bhaṇanti evaṃ dīpayanti evaṃ voharantīti– nāññesu dhammesu visuddhimāhu. "
