793955,149,908,10,17,1,65,7,Taṃ jayatthaṃ pappuyya pāpuṇitvā adhigantvā vinditvā paṭilabhitvā. 
793956,149,908,18,43,1,120,20,"Yathā mano {ahū}ti yathā mano ahu, yathā citto ahu, yathā saṅkappo ahu, yathā viññāṇo ahūti– pappuyya tamatthaṃ yathā mano ahu. "
