793979,149,925,2,7,1,31,4,Sūro yathā rājakhādāya {puṭṭho}ti. 
793980,149,925,8,17,1,58,8,{Sūro}ti sūro vīro vikkanto abhīrū achambhī anutrāsī apalāyī. 
793981,149,925,18,33,1,115,12,Rājakhādāya {puṭṭho}ti rājakhādanīyena rājabhojanīyena puṭṭho posito apādito vaḍḍhitoti– sūro yathā rājakhādāya puṭṭho. 
793982,149,926,2,5,1,32,3,Abhigajjameti paṭisūramicchan ti. 
793983,149,926,6,25,1,187,18,So gajjanto uggajjanto abhigajjanto eti upeti upagacchati paṭisūraṃ paṭipurisaṃ paṭisattuṃ paṭimallaṃ icchanto sādiyanto patthayanto pihayanto abhijappantoti– abhigajjameti paṭisūramicchaṃ. 
