793985,149,927,9,36,1,149,22,"Yeneva so diṭṭhigatiko tena palehi, tena vaja, tena gaccha, tena atikkama, so tuyhaṃ paṭisūro paṭipuriso paṭisattu paṭimalloti– yeneva so tena palehi sūra. "
