793987,149,928,8,33,1,211,23,"Pubbeva bodhiyā mūle ye paṭisenikarā kilesā paṭilomakarā paṭikaṇḍakakarā paṭipakkhakarā te natthi na santi na saṃvijjanti nupalabbhanti, pahīnā samucchinnā vūpasantā paṭipassaddhā abhabbuppattikā ñāṇagginā daḍḍhā. "
