793995,149,935,2,30,1,236,23,"Ye diṭṭhimuggayha {vivādayantī}ti ye dvāsaṭṭhidiṭṭhigatānaṃ aññataraññataraṃ diṭṭhigataṃ gahetvā gaṇhitvā uggaṇhitvā parāmasitvā abhinivisitvā vivādayanti kalahaṃ karonti bhaṇḍanaṃ karonti ‘ viggahaṃ karonti vivādaṃ karonti, medhagaṃ karonti–"
793996,149,935,31,98,1,373,48,"‘‘ na tvaṃ imaṃ dhammavinayaṃ ājānāsi, ahaṃ imaṃ dhammavinayaṃ ājānāmi, kiṃ tvaṃ imaṃ dhammavinayaṃ ājānissasi, micchāpaṭipanno tvamasi, ahamasmi sammāpaṭipanno, sahitaṃ me, asahitaṃ te, pure vacanīyaṃ pacchā avaca, pacchā vacanīyaṃ pure avaca, adhiciṇṇaṃ te viparāvattaṃ, āropito te vādo, niggahito tvamasi, cara vādappamokkhāya, nibbeṭhehi vā sace pahosī’’ ti– ye diṭṭhimuggayha vivādayanti. "
793997,149,936,2,7,1,31,4,Idameva saccanti ca {vādayantī}ti.
793998,149,936,8,24,1,90,11,"‘‘ Sassato loko, idameva saccaṃ moghamaññan’’ ti vādayanti kathenti bhaṇanti dīpayanti voharanti."
