794019,149,949,2,6,1,32,3,Diṭṭhīhi diṭṭhiṃ {avirujjhamānā}ti. 
794020,149,949,7,31,1,246,21,"Yesaṃ dvāsaṭṭhi diṭṭhigatāni pahīnāni samucchinnāni vūpasantāni paṭipassaddhāni abhabbuppattikāni ñāṇagginā daḍḍhāni, te diṭṭhīhi diṭṭhiṃ avirujjhamānā appaṭivirujjhamānā appahīyamānā appaṭihaññamānā appaṭihatamānāti– diṭṭhīhi diṭṭhiṃ avirujjhamānā. "
