794612,149,1195,2,9,1,35,4,"Nirāsatti anāgate, atītaṃ nānusocati; "
794613,149,1196,2,9,1,42,6,"Vivekadassī phassesu, diṭṭhīsu ca na nīyati. "
794614,149,1197,2,5,1,19,2,Nirāsatti {anāgate}ti. 
794615,149,1197,6,9,1,20,3,Āsatti vuccati taṇhā. 
794616,149,1197,10,19,1,45,7,Yo rāgo sārāgo… pe… abhijjhā lobho akusalamūlaṃ. 
794617,149,1197,20,30,1,98,10,Yassesā āsatti taṇhā pahīnā samucchinnā vūpasantā paṭipassaddhā abhabbuppattikā ñāṇagginā daḍḍhāti. 
794618,149,1197,31,34,1,24,3,Evampi nirāsatti anāgate. 
794619,149,1197,35,71,1,190,24,"Atha vā‘‘ evaṃrūpo siyaṃ anāgatamaddhānan’’ ti tattha nandiṃ na samannāneti,‘‘ evaṃvedano siyaṃ… evaṃsañño siyaṃ… evaṃsaṅkhāro siyaṃ… evaṃviññāṇo siyaṃ anāgatamaddhānan’’ ti tattha nandiṃ na samannāneti. "
794620,149,1197,72,75,1,24,3,Evampi nirāsatti anāgate. 
794621,149,1197,76,102,1,149,19,"Atha vā‘‘ iti me cakkhu siyā anāgatamaddhānaṃ– iti rūpā’’ ti appaṭiladdhassa paṭilābhāya cittaṃ na paṇidahati , cetaso appaṇidhānappaccayā na tadabhinandati; "
794622,149,1197,103,105,1,18,2,na tadabhinandanto. 
794623,149,1197,106,109,1,24,3,Evampi nirāsatti anāgate.
794624,149,1197,110,150,1,192,26,"‘‘ Iti me sotaṃ siyā anāgatamaddhānaṃ– iti saddā’’ ti… pe…‘‘ iti me mano siyā anāgatamaddhānaṃ– iti dhammā’’ ti appaṭiladdhassa paṭilābhāya cittaṃ na paṇidahati, cetaso appaṇidhānappaccayā na tadabhinandati; "
794625,149,1197,151,153,1,18,2,na tadabhinandanto. 
794626,149,1197,154,157,1,24,3,Evampi nirāsatti anāgate. 
794627,149,1197,158,189,1,195,26,"Atha vā‘‘ imināhaṃ sīlena vā vatena vā tapena vā brahmacariyena vā devo vā bhavissāmi devaññataro vā’’ ti appaṭiladdhassa paṭilābhāya cittaṃ na paṇidahati, cetaso appaṇidhānappaccayā na tadabhinandati; "
794628,149,1197,190,192,1,18,2,na tadabhinandanto. 
794629,149,1197,193,196,1,24,3,Evampi nirāsatti anāgate. 
794630,149,1198,2,5,1,19,2,Atītaṃ {nānusocatī}ti. 
794631,149,1198,6,139,1,534,92,"Vipariṇataṃ vā vatthuṃ na socati, vipariṇatasmiṃ vā vatthusmiṃ na socati,‘‘ cakkhu me vipariṇatan’’ ti na socati,‘‘ sotaṃ me… ghānaṃ me… jivhā me… kāyo me… rūpā me… saddā me… gandhā me… rasā me… phoṭṭhabbā me… kulaṃ me… gaṇo me… āvāso me… lābho me… yaso me… pasaṃsā me… sukhaṃ me… cīvaraṃ me… piṇḍapāto me… senāsanaṃ me… gilānapaccayabhesajjaparikkhāro me… mātā me… pitā me… bhātā me… bhaginī me… putto me… dhītā me… mittā me… amaccā me… ñātakā me… sālohitā me vipariṇatā’’ ti na socati na kilamati na paridevati na urattāḷiṃ kandati na sammohaṃ āpajjatīti– atītaṃ nānusocati. "
794632,149,1199,2,7,1,22,2,Vivekadassī {phassesū}ti. 
794633,149,1199,8,58,1,424,42,"Cakkhusamphasso sotasamphasso ghānasamphasso jivhāsamphasso kāyasamphasso manosamphasso, adhivacanasamphasso paṭighasamphasso, sukhavedanīyo phasso dukkhavedanīyo phasso adukkhamasukhavedanīyo phasso, kusalo phasso akusalo phasso abyākato phasso, kāmāvacaro phasso rūpāvacaro phasso arūpāvacaro phasso, suññato phasso animitto phasso appaṇihito phasso, lokiyo phasso lokuttaro phasso, atīto phasso anāgato phasso paccuppanno phasso; "
794634,149,1199,59,69,1,71,9,yo evarūpo phasso phusanā samphusanā samphusitattaṃ– ayaṃ vuccati phasso. 
794635,149,1200,2,5,1,22,2,Vivekadassī {phassesū}ti. 
794636,149,1200,6,94,1,656,70,"Cakkhusamphassaṃ vivittaṃ passati attena vā attaniyena vā niccena vā dhuvena vā sassatena vā avipariṇāmadhammena vā, sotasamphassaṃ vivittaṃ passati… ghānasamphassaṃ vivittaṃ passati… jivhāsamphassaṃ vivittaṃ passati… kāyasamphassaṃ vivittaṃ passati… manosamphassaṃ vivittaṃ passati… adhivacanasamphassaṃ vivittaṃ passati… paṭighasamphassaṃ vivittaṃ passati… sukhavedanīyaṃ phassaṃ… dukkhavedanīyaṃ phassaṃ… adukkhamasukhavedanīyaṃ phassaṃ… kusalaṃ phassaṃ… akusalaṃ phassaṃ… abyākataṃ phassaṃ… kāmāvacaraṃ phassaṃ… rūpāvacaraṃ phassaṃ… arūpāvacaraṃ phassaṃ… lokiyaṃ phassaṃ vivittaṃ passati attena vā attaniyena vā niccena vā dhuvena vā sassatena vā avipariṇāmadhammena vā. "
794637,149,1201,2,34,1,220,29,"Atha vā atītaṃ phassaṃ anāgatehi ca paccuppannehi ca phassehi vivittaṃ passati, anāgataṃ phassaṃ atītehi ca paccuppannehi ca phassehi vivittaṃ passati, paccuppannaṃ phassaṃ atītehi ca anāgatehi ca phassehi vivittaṃ passati. "
794638,149,1201,35,77,1,380,40,"Atha vā ye te phassā ariyā anāsavā lokuttarā suññatapaṭisaññuttā, te phasse vivitte passati rāgena dosena mohena kodhena upanāhena makkhena paḷāsena issāya macchariyena māyāya sāṭheyyena thambhena sārambhena mānena atimānena madena pamādena sabbakilesehi sabbaduccaritehi sabbadarathehi sabbapariḷāhehi sabbasantāpehi sabbākusalābhisaṅkhārehi vivitte passatīti– vivekadassī phassesu. "
794639,149,1202,2,7,1,23,4,Diṭṭhīsu ca na {nīyatī}ti. 
794640,149,1202,8,18,1,116,10,Tassa dvāsaṭṭhi diṭṭhigatāni pahīnāni samucchinnāni vūpasantāni paṭipassaddhāni abhabbuppattikāni ñāṇagginā daḍḍhāni. 
794641,149,1202,19,30,1,57,10,So diṭṭhiyā na yāyati na nīyati na vuyhati na saṃharīyati; 
794642,149,1202,31,43,1,76,11,napi taṃ diṭṭhigataṃ sārato pacceti na paccāgacchatīti– diṭṭhīsu ca na nīyati. 
794643,149,1203,2,5,1,14,2,Tenāha bhagavā–
