794645,149,1205,2,12,1,45,7,"Vivekadassī phassesu, diṭṭhīsu ca na nīyatī’’ ti. "
794646,149,1206,2,5,1,0,0,87. 
794647,149,1207,2,7,1,34,4,"Patilīno akuhako, apihālu amaccharī; "
794648,149,1208,2,9,1,41,6,"Appagabbho ajeguccho, pesuṇeyye ca no yuto. "
794649,149,1209,2,5,1,18,2,Patilīno {akuhako}ti. 
794650,149,1209,6,38,1,200,20,"{Patilīno}ti rāgassa pahīnattā patilīno, dosassa pahīnattā patilīno, mohassa pahīnattā patilīno, kodhassa… upanāhassa … makkhassa… paḷāsassa… issāya… macchariyassa… pe… sabbākusalābhisaṅkhārānaṃ pahīnattā patilīno. "
794651,149,1209,39,41,1,21,2,Vuttañhetaṃ bhagavatā–
794652,149,1209,42,51,1,40,5,"‘‘ kathañca, bhikkhave, bhikkhu patilīno hoti? "
794653,149,1209,52,65,1,111,11,"Imassa, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno asmimāno pahīno hoti ucchinnamūlo tālāvatthukato anabhāvaṃkato āyatiṃ anuppādadhammo. "
794654,149,1209,66,79,1,52,8,"Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu patilīno hotī’’ ti– patilīno. "
794655,149,1210,2,15,1,139,9,"{Akuhako}ti tīṇi kuhanavatthūni– paccayapaṭisevanasaṅkhātaṃ kuhanavatthu, iriyāpathasaṅkhātaṃ kuhanavatthu, sāmantajappanasaṅkhātaṃ kuhanavatthu. "
794656,149,1211,2,5,1,47,3,Katamaṃ paccayapaṭisevanasaṅkhātaṃ kuhanavatthu? 
794657,149,1211,6,11,1,92,5,Idha gahapatikā bhikkhuṃ nimantenti cīvarapiṇḍapātasenāsanagilānapaccayabhesajjaparikkhārehi. 
794658,149,1211,12,30,1,222,15,"So pāpiccho icchāpakato atthiko cīvarapiṇḍapātasenāsanagilānapaccayabhesajjaparikkhārānaṃ bhiyyokamyataṃ upādāya cīvaraṃ paccakkhāti, piṇḍapātaṃ paccakkhāti, senāsanaṃ paccakkhāti, gilānapaccayabhesajjaparikkhāraṃ paccakkhāti. "
794659,149,1211,31,33,1,10,2,So evamāha–
794660,149,1211,34,40,1,33,4,‘‘ kiṃ samaṇassa mahagghena cīvarena! 
794661,149,1211,41,56,1,106,15,Etaṃ sāruppaṃ yaṃ samaṇo susānā vā saṅkārakūṭā vā pāpaṇikā vā nantakāni uccinitvā saṅghāṭiṃ katvā dhāreyya. 
794662,149,1211,57,62,1,36,4,Kiṃ samaṇassa mahagghena piṇḍapātena ! 
794663,149,1211,63,71,1,69,8,Etaṃ sāruppaṃ yaṃ samaṇo uñchācariyāya piṇḍiyālopena jīvikaṃ kappeyya. 
794664,149,1211,72,76,1,35,4,Kiṃ samaṇassa mahagghena senāsanena! 
794665,149,1211,77,89,1,72,11,Etaṃ sāruppaṃ yaṃ samaṇo rukkhamūliko vā assa sosāniko vā abbhokāsiko vā. 
794666,149,1211,90,94,1,58,4,Kiṃ samaṇassa mahagghena gilānapaccayabhesajjaparikkhārena! 
794667,149,1211,95,108,1,78,11,Etaṃ sāruppaṃ yaṃ samaṇo pūtimuttena vā haritakīkhaṇḍena vā osadhaṃ kareyyā’’ ti. 
794668,149,1211,109,126,1,143,13,"Tadupādāya lūkhaṃ cīvaraṃ dhāreti, lūkhaṃ piṇḍapātaṃ paribhuñjati, lūkhaṃ senāsanaṃ paṭisevati , lūkhaṃ gilānapaccayabhesajjaparikkhāraṃ paṭisevati. "
