794694,149,1215,2,5,1,19,2,Apihālu {amaccharī}ti. 
794695,149,1215,6,9,1,18,3,Pihā vuccati taṇhā. 
794696,149,1215,10,19,1,45,7,Yo rāgo sārāgo… pe… abhijjhā lobho akusalamūlaṃ. 
794697,149,1215,20,34,1,113,13,"Yassesā pihā taṇhā pahīnā samucchinnā vūpasantā paṭipassaddhā abhabbuppattikā ñāṇagginā daḍḍhā, so vuccati apihālu. "
794698,149,1215,35,114,1,452,46,"So rūpe na piheti, sadde… gandhe… rase… phoṭṭhabbe… kulaṃ… gaṇaṃ… āvāsaṃ… lābhaṃ… yasaṃ… pasaṃsaṃ… sukhaṃ… cīvaraṃ… piṇḍapātaṃ… senāsanaṃ… gilānapaccayabhesajjaparikkhāraṃ… kāmadhātuṃ… rūpadhātuṃ… arūpadhātuṃ… kāmabhavaṃ… rūpabhavaṃ… arūpabhavaṃ… saññābhavaṃ… asaññābhavaṃ … nevasaññānāsaññābhavaṃ… ekavokārabhavaṃ… catuvokārabhavaṃ… pañcavokārabhavaṃ… atītaṃ… anāgataṃ… paccuppannaṃ… diṭṭhasutamutaviññātabbe dhamme na piheti na icchati na sādiyati na pattheti nābhijappatīti– apihālu. "
794699,149,1215,115,129,1,115,8,"{Amaccharī}ti pañca macchariyāni– āvāsamacchariyaṃ, kulamacchariyaṃ, lābhamacchariyaṃ, vaṇṇamacchariyaṃ, dhammamacchariyaṃ. "
