794703,149,1216,2,6,1,22,2,Appagabbho {ajeguccho}ti. 
794704,149,1216,7,19,1,95,9,"Pāgabbhiyanti tīṇi pāgabbhiyāni– kāyikaṃ pāgabbhiyaṃ, vācasikaṃ pāgabbhiyaṃ, cetasikaṃ pāgabbhiyaṃ. "
794705,149,1216,20,23,1,27,3,Katamaṃ kāyikaṃ pāgabbhiyaṃ? 
794706,149,1216,24,62,1,322,31,"Idhekacco saṅghagatopi kāyikaṃ pāgabbhiyaṃ dasseti, gaṇagatopi kāyikaṃ pāgabbhiyaṃ dasseti, bhojanasālāyampi kāyikaṃ pāgabbhiyaṃ dasseti, jantāgharepi kāyikaṃ pāgabbhiyaṃ dasseti, udakatitthepi kāyikaṃ pāgabbhiyaṃ dasseti, antaragharaṃ pavisantopi kāyikaṃ pāgabbhiyaṃ dasseti, antaragharaṃ paviṭṭhopi kāyikaṃ pāgabbhiyaṃ dasseti. "
794707,149,1217,2,7,1,45,5,Kathaṃ saṅghagato kāyikaṃ pāgabbhiyaṃ dasseti? 
794708,149,1217,8,48,1,225,23,"Idhekacco saṅghagato acittīkārakato [ acittikārakato( syā. ka.)] there bhikkhū ghaṭṭayantopi tiṭṭhati, ghaṭṭayantopi nisīdati, puratopi tiṭṭhati, puratopi nisīdati, uccepi āsane nisīdati, sasīsaṃ pārupitvāpi nisīdati, ṭhitakopi bhaṇati, bāhāvikkhepakopi bhaṇati. "
