794748,149,1229,2,5,1,11,1,{Ajeguccho}ti . 
794749,149,1229,6,12,1,38,5,"Atthi puggalo jeguccho, atthi ajeguccho. "
794750,149,1229,13,17,1,26,4,Katamo ca puggalo jeguccho? 
794751,149,1229,18,37,1,198,18,Idhekacco puggalo dussīlo hoti pāpadhammo asucisaṅkassarasamācāro paṭicchannakammanto assamaṇo samaṇapaṭiñño abrahmacārī brahmacāripaṭiñño antopūti avassuto kasambujāto– ayaṃ vuccati puggalo jeguccho. 
794752,149,1229,38,61,1,169,20,"Atha vā kodhano hoti upāyāsabahulo, appampi vutto samāno abhisajjati kuppati byāpajjati patiṭṭhīyati, kopañca dosañca appaccayañca pātukaroti– ayaṃ vuccati puggalo jeguccho. "
794753,149,1229,62,105,1,214,28,"Atha vā kodhano hoti upanāhī, makkhī hoti paḷāsī, issukī hoti maccharī, saṭho hoti māyāvī , thaddho hoti atimānī, pāpiccho hoti micchādiṭṭhi[ micchādiṭṭhī( sī.)], sandiṭṭhiparāmāsī hoti ādānaggāhī duppaṭinissaggī– ayaṃ vuccati puggalo jeguccho. "
794754,149,1230,2,6,1,27,4,Katamo ca puggalo ajeguccho? 
794755,149,1230,7,27,1,172,17,"Idha bhikkhu sīlavā hoti pātimokkhasaṃvarasaṃvuto viharati ācāragocarasampanno aṇumattesu vajjesu bhayadassāvī, samādāya sikkhati sikkhāpadesu– ayaṃ vuccati puggalo ajeguccho. "
794756,149,1230,28,56,1,189,25,"Atha vā akkodhano hoti anupāyāsabahulo, bahumpi vutto samāno na abhisajjati na kuppati na byāpajjati na patiṭṭhīyati, na kopañca dosañca appaccayañca pātukaroti– ayaṃ vuccati puggalo ajeguccho. "
794757,149,1230,57,95,1,238,30,"Atha vā akkodhano hoti anupanāhī, amakkhī hoti apaḷāsī, anissukī hoti amaccharī, asaṭho hoti amāyāvī, athaddho hoti anatimānī , na pāpiccho hoti na micchādiṭṭhi, asandiṭṭhiparāmāsī hoti anādānaggāhī suppaṭinissaggī– ayaṃ vuccati puggalo ajeguccho. "
794758,149,1230,96,108,1,110,10,"Sabbe bālaputhujjanā jegucchā, puthujjanakalyāṇakaṃ upādāya aṭṭha ariyapuggalā ajegucchāti– appagabbho ajeguccho. "
794759,149,1231,2,7,1,22,4,Pesuṇeyye ca no {yuto}ti. 
794760,149,1231,8,28,1,122,17,"Pesuññanti idhekacco pisuṇavāco hoti, ito sutvā amutra akkhātā imesaṃ bhedāya, amutra vā sutvā imesaṃ akkhātā amūsaṃ bhedāya. "
794761,149,1231,29,59,1,133,17,"Iti samaggānaṃ vā bhettā[ bhedo( ka.)], bhinnānaṃ vā anuppadātā, vaggārāmo, vaggarato, vagganandī, vaggakaraṇiṃ vācaṃ bhāsitā hoti– idaṃ vuccati pesuññaṃ. "
794762,149,1232,2,20,1,79,10,"Api ca dvīhi kāraṇehi pesuññaṃ upasaṃharati– piyakamyatāya vā, bhedādhippāyena[ bhedādhippāyo( bahūsu)] vā. "
794763,149,1232,21,25,1,42,4,Kathaṃ piyakamyatāya pesuññaṃ upasaṃharati? 
