794769,149,1232,93,119,1,175,23,"Yassetaṃ pesuññaṃ pahīnaṃ samucchinnaṃ vūpasantaṃ paṭipassaddhaṃ abhabbuppattikaṃ ñāṇagginā daḍḍhaṃ, so pesuññe no yuto na yutto na payutto na sammāyuttoti– pesuṇeyye ca no yuto. "
