794862,149,1263,11,58,1,302,34,"{Viruddho}ti yo cittassa āghāto paṭighāto, paṭighaṃ paṭivirodho, kopo pakopo sampakopo, doso padoso sampadoso, cittassa byāpatti manopadoso, kodho kujjhanā kujjhitattaṃ, doso dussanā dussitattaṃ, byāpatti byāpajjanā byāpajjitattaṃ virodho paṭivirodho, caṇḍikkaṃ, asuropo, anattamanatā cittassa– ayaṃ vuccati virodho. "
