795077,149,1343,57,123,1,398,52,"Dhammesu ca na {gacchatī}ti na chandāgatiṃ gacchati, na dosāgatiṃ gacchati, na mohāgatiṃ gacchati, na bhayāgatiṃ gacchati, na rāgavasena gacchati, na dosavasena gacchati, na mohavasena gacchati, na mānavasena gacchati, na diṭṭhivasena gacchati, na uddhaccavasena gacchati, na vicikicchāvasena gacchati, na anusayavasena gacchati na ca vaggehi dhammehi yāyati nīyati vuyhati saṃharīyatīti– dhammesu ca na gacchati. "
