795099,149,1356,2,6,1,30,3,Paridevasokā sahamaccharā {cā}ti. 
795100,149,1356,7,55,1,365,36,"{Paridevo}ti ñātibyasanena vā phuṭṭhassa, bhogabyasanena vā phuṭṭhassa, rogabyasanena vā phuṭṭhassa, sīlabyasanena vā phuṭṭhassa, diṭṭhibyasanena vā phuṭṭhassa, aññataraññatarena vā byasanena samannāgatassa, aññataraññatarena vā dukkhadhammena phuṭṭhassa, ādevo paridevo, ādevanā paridevanā, ādevitattaṃ paridevitattaṃ, vācā palāpo vippalāpo lālappo lālappāyanā lālappāyitattaṃ. "
795101,149,1356,56,90,1,279,26,"{Soko}ti ñātibyasanena vā phuṭṭhassa, bhogarogasīladiṭṭhibyasanena vā phuṭṭhassa, aññataraññatarena vā byasanena samannāgatassa, aññataraññatarena vā dukkhadhammena phuṭṭhassa, soko socanā socitattaṃ, antosoko antoparisoko, antoḍāho antopariḍāho, cetaso parijjhāyanā domanassaṃ sokasallaṃ. "
795102,149,1356,91,105,1,116,9,"Maccharan ti pañca macchariyāni– āvāsamacchariyaṃ, kulamacchariyaṃ, lābhamacchariyaṃ, vaṇṇamacchariyaṃ, dhammamacchariyaṃ. "
