795326,149,1431,15,17,1,21,2,Katamā adhisīlasikkhā? 
795327,149,1431,18,55,1,295,30,"Idha bhikkhu sīlavā hoti, pātimokkhasaṃvarasaṃvuto viharati ācāragocarasampanno, aṇumattesu vajjesu bhayadassāvī, samādāya sikkhati sikkhāpadesu, khuddako sīlakkhandho… mahanto sīlakkhandho… sīlaṃ patiṭṭhā ādi caraṇaṃ saṃyamo saṃvaro mukhaṃ pamukhaṃ kusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ samāpattiyā– ayaṃ adhisīlasikkhā. "
795328,149,1431,56,58,1,22,2,Katamā adhicittasikkhā? 
795329,149,1431,59,73,1,91,11,Idha bhikkhu vivicceva kāmehi… pe… catutthaṃ jhānaṃ upasampajja viharati– ayaṃ adhicittasikkhā. 
795330,149,1431,74,76,1,22,2,Katamā adhipaññāsikkhā? 
795331,149,1431,77,88,1,110,10,"Idha bhikkhu paññavā hoti, udayatthagāminiyā paññāya samannāgato ariyāya nibbedhikāya sammādukkhakkhayagāminiyā. "
795332,149,1431,89,138,1,215,27,"So‘‘ idaṃ dukkhan’’ ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti… pe…‘‘ ayaṃ dukkhanirodhagāminī paṭipadā’’ ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti,‘‘ ime āsavā’’ ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti… pe…‘‘ ayaṃ āsavanirodhagāminī paṭipadā’’ ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti– ayaṃ adhipaññāsikkhā. "
