795785,149,1664,12,59,1,326,39,"Ito aññaṃ dhammaṃ diṭṭhiṃ paṭipadaṃ maggaṃ ye abhivadanti, te suddhimaggaṃ visuddhimaggaṃ parisuddhimaggaṃ vodātamaggaṃ pariyodātamaggaṃ viraddhā aparaddhā khalitā galitā aññāya aparaddhā akevalī te, asamattā te, aparipuṇṇā te, hīnā nihīnā omakā lāmakā chatukkā parittāti– aññaṃ ito yābhivadanti dhammaṃ, aparaddhā suddhimakevalī te. "
