795926,149,1736,27,57,1,124,18,"Idha, gahapati, na kāyena pāpakammaṃ karoti, na pāpikaṃ[ pāpakaṃ( sī.)] vācaṃ bhāsati, na pāpakaṃ saṅkappaṃ saṅkappeti, na pāpakaṃ ājīvaṃ ājīvati. "
