795953,149,1746,126,140,1,123,12,"Sīlaṃ anabhisambhuṇanto sīlato cavati, vataṃ anabhisambhuṇanto vatato cavati, sīlabbataṃ anabhisambhuṇanto sīlabbatato cavati. "
