796793,149,2097,2,6,1,16,2,Na {pādalolassā}ti. 
796794,149,2097,7,10,1,20,3,Kathaṃ pādalolo hoti? 
796795,149,2097,11,33,1,206,22,Idhekacco pādaloliyena samannāgato hoti ārāmena ārāmaṃ uyyānena uyyānaṃ gāmena gāmaṃ nigamena nigamaṃ nagarena nagaraṃ raṭṭhena raṭṭhaṃ janapadena janapadaṃ dīghacārikaṃ anavaṭṭhitacārikaṃ anuyutto viharati. 
796796,149,2097,34,37,1,20,3,Evampi pādalolo hoti. 
796797,149,2098,2,9,1,62,7,Atha vā bhikkhu antopisaṅghārāme pādaloliyena samannāgato hoti. 
796798,149,2098,10,63,1,470,51,Na atthahetu na kāraṇahetu uddhato avūpasantacitto pariveṇato pariveṇaṃ gacchati vihārato vihāraṃ gacchati aḍḍhayogato aḍḍhayogaṃ gacchati pāsādato pāsādaṃ gacchati hammiyato hammiyaṃ gacchati guhāya guhaṃ gacchati leṇato leṇaṃ gacchati kuṭito kuṭiṃ gacchati kūṭāgārato kūṭāgāraṃ gacchati aṭṭato aṭṭaṃ gacchati māḷato māḷaṃ gacchati uddaṇḍato uddaṇḍaṃ gacchati upaṭṭhānasālato upaṭṭhānasālaṃ gacchati maṇḍalamāḷato maṇḍalamāḷaṃ gacchati rukkhamūlato rukkhamūlaṃ gacchati. 
796799,149,2098,64,87,1,123,20,"Yattha vā pana bhikkhū nisīdanti tahiṃ gacchati, tattha ekassa vā dutiyo hoti, dvinnaṃ vā tatiyo hoti, tiṇṇaṃ vā catuttho hoti. "
796800,149,2098,88,125,1,413,35,"Tattha bahuṃ samphappalāpaṃ palapati, seyyathidaṃ– rājakathaṃ corakathaṃ mahāmattakathaṃ senākathaṃ bhayakathaṃ yuddhakathaṃ annakathaṃ pānakathaṃ vatthakathaṃ yānakathaṃ sayanakathaṃ mālākathaṃ gandhakathaṃ ñātikathaṃ gāmakathaṃ nigamakathaṃ nagarakathaṃ janapadakathaṃ itthikathaṃ sūrakathaṃ visikhākathaṃ kumbhaṭṭhānakathaṃ pubbapetakathaṃ nānattakathaṃ lokakkhāyikaṃ samuddakkhāyikaṃ iti bhavābhavakathaṃ iti vā. "
796801,149,2098,126,129,1,20,3,Evampi pādalolo hoti. 
796802,149,2099,2,6,1,16,2,Na {pādalolassā}ti. 
796803,149,2099,7,55,1,438,43,"Pādaloliyaṃ pajaheyya vinodeyya byantiṃ kareyya anabhāvaṃ gameyya, pādaloliyā ārato assa virato paṭivirato nikkhanto nissaṭo vippamutto visaññutto vimariyādikatena cetasā vihareyya careyya vicareyya iriyeyya vatteyya pāleyya yapeyya yāpeyya, paṭisallānārāmo assa paṭisallānarato ajjhattaṃ cetosamathamanuyutto anirākatajjhāno vipassanā samannāgato brūhetā suññāgārānaṃ jhāyī jhānarato ekattamanuyutto paramatthagarukoti– jhāyī na pādalolassa. "
796804,149,2100,2,6,1,31,3,Virame kukkuccā {nappamajjeyyā}ti. 
796805,149,2100,7,42,1,293,27,"Kukkuccan ti hatthakukkuccampi kukkuccaṃ, pādakukkuccampi kukkuccaṃ, hatthapādakukkuccampi kukkuccaṃ, akappiye kappiyasaññitā, kappiye akappiyasaññitā, avajje vajjasaññitā, vajje avajjasaññitā, yaṃ evarūpaṃ kukkuccaṃ kukkuccāyanā kukkuccāyitattaṃ cetaso vippaṭisāro manovilekho– idaṃ vuccati kukkuccaṃ. "
796806,149,2101,2,16,1,95,13,Api ca dvīhi kāraṇehi uppajjati kukkuccaṃ cetaso vippaṭisāro manovilekho– katattā ca akatattā ca. 
796807,149,2101,17,27,1,80,10,Kathaṃ katattā ca akatattā ca uppajjati kukkuccaṃ cetaso vippaṭisāro manovilekho?
796808,149,2101,28,147,1,595,79,"‘‘ Kataṃ me kāyaduccaritaṃ, akataṃ me kāyasucaritan’’ ti uppajjati kukkuccaṃ cetaso vippaṭisāro manovilekho,‘‘ kataṃ me vacīduccaritaṃ, akataṃ me vacīsucaritan’’ ti uppajjati kukkuccaṃ cetaso vippaṭisāro manovilekho,‘‘ kataṃ me manoduccaritaṃ, akataṃ me manosucaritanti… pe…‘‘ kato me pāṇātipāto, akatā me pāṇātipātā veramaṇī’’ ti uppajjati kukkuccaṃ… pe… manovilekho,‘‘ kataṃ me adinnādānaṃ… kato me kāmesumicchācāro… kato me musāvādo… katā me pisuṇavācā… katā me pharusavācā… kato me samphappalāpo… katā me abhijjhā… kato me byāpādo… katā me micchādiṭṭhi, akatā me sammādiṭṭhī’’ ti uppajjati kukkuccaṃ cetaso vippaṭisāro manovilekho . "
796809,149,2101,148,158,1,78,10,Evaṃ katattā ca akatattā ca uppajjati kukkuccaṃ cetaso vippaṭisāro manovilekho. 
796810,149,2102,2,165,1,591,81,"Atha vā‘‘ sīlesumhi na paripūrakārī’’ ti uppajjati kukkuccaṃ cetaso vippaṭisāro manovilekho,‘‘ indriyesumhi aguttadvāro’’ ti… pe…‘‘ bhojane amattaññumhī’’ ti…‘‘ jāgariyaṃ ananuyuttomhī’’ ti…‘‘ na satisampajaññena samannāgatomhī’’ ti…‘‘ abhāvitā me cattāro satipaṭṭhānā’’ ti…‘‘ abhāvitā me cattāro sammappadhānā’’ ti…‘‘ abhāvitā me cattāro iddhipādā’’ ti…‘‘ abhāvitāni me pañcindriyānī’’ ti…‘‘ abhāvitāni me pañca balānī’’ ti…‘‘ abhāvitā me satta bojjhaṅgā’’ ti…‘‘ abhāvito me ariyo aṭṭhaṅgiko maggo’’ ti…‘‘ dukkhaṃ me apariññātan’’ ti…‘‘ samudayo me appahīno’’ ti…‘‘ maggo me abhāvito’’ ti…‘‘ nirodho me asacchikato’’ ti uppajjati kukkuccaṃ cetaso vippaṭisāro manovilekho. "
796811,149,2102,166,180,1,123,13,Virame {kukkuccā}ti kukkuccā ārameyya virameyya paṭivirameyya kukkuccaṃ pajaheyya vinodeyya byantiṃ kareyya anabhāvaṃ gameyya. 
796812,149,2102,181,196,1,129,14,Kukkuccā ārato assa virato paṭivirato nikkhanto nissaṭo vippamutto visaññutto vimariyādikatena cetasā vihareyyāti– virame kukkuccā. 
796813,149,2103,2,14,1,133,11,{Nappamajjeyyā}ti sakkaccakārī assa sātaccakārī aṭṭhitakārī anolīnavuttiko anikkhittacchando anikkhittadhuro appamādo kusalesu dhammesu.
796814,149,2103,15,33,1,114,13,"‘‘ Kadāhaṃ aparipūraṃ vā sīlakkhandhaṃ paripūreyyaṃ, paripūraṃ vā sīlakkhandhaṃ tattha tattha paññāya anuggaṇheyyan’’ ti? "
796815,149,2103,34,60,1,159,24,Yo tattha chando ca vāyāmo ca ussāho ca ussoḷhī ca thāmo ca appaṭivānī ca sati ca sampajaññañca ātappaṃ padhānaṃ adhiṭṭhānaṃ anuyogo appamādo kusalesu dhammesu .
796816,149,2103,61,99,1,248,26,"‘‘ Kadāhaṃ aparipūraṃ vā samādhikkhandhaṃ… pe… paññākkhandhaṃ… vimuttikkhandhaṃ… vimuttiñāṇadassanakkhandhaṃ… kadāhaṃ apariññātaṃ vā dukkhaṃ parijāneyyaṃ, appahīne vā kilese pajaheyyaṃ, abhāvitaṃ vā maggaṃ bhāveyyaṃ, asacchikataṃ vā nirodhaṃ sacchikareyyan’’ ti? "
796817,149,2103,100,129,1,191,27,Yo tattha chando ca vāyāmo ca ussāho ca ussoḷhī ca thāmo ca appaṭivānī ca sati ca sampajaññañca ātappaṃ padhānaṃ adhiṭṭhānaṃ anuyogo appamādo kusalesu dhammesūti– virame kukkuccā nappamajjeyya. 
796818,149,2104,2,9,1,51,5,"Athāsanesu sayanesu, appasaddesu bhikkhu {vihareyyā}ti. "
796819,149,2104,10,29,1,132,15,{Athā}ti padasandhi… pe… āsanaṃ vuccati yattha nisīdati– mañco pīṭhaṃ bhisi taṭṭikā cammakhaṇḍo tiṇasanthāro paṇṇasanthāro palālasanthāro. 
796820,149,2104,30,41,1,85,10,Sayanaṃ vuccati senāsanaṃ vihāro aḍḍhayogo pāsādo hammiyaṃ guhāti– athāsanesu sayanesu. 
796821,149,2105,2,6,1,31,3,Appasaddesu bhikkhu {vihareyyā}ti. 
796822,149,2105,7,27,1,215,19,Appasaddesu appanigghosesu vijanavātesu manussarāhasseyyakesu paṭisallānasāruppesu senāsanesu careyya vicareyya vihareyya iriyeyya vatteyya pāleyya yapeyya yāpeyyāti– athāsanesu sayanesu appasaddesu bhikkhu vihareyya. 
