796913,149,2144,2,5,1,23,2,Nindāya {nappavedheyyā}ti. 
796914,149,2144,6,76,1,546,65,"Idhekacce bhikkhū nindanti jātiyā vā gottena vā kolaputtiyena vā vaṇṇapokkharatāya vā dhanena vā ajjhenena vā kammāyatanena vā sippāyatanena vā vijjāṭṭhānena vā sutena vā paṭibhānena vā aññataraññatarena vā vatthunā nindanti garahanti upavadanti, nindito garahito upavadito nindāya garahāya upavādena akittiyā avaṇṇahārikāya na vedheyya nappavedheyya na sampavedheyya na taseyya na uttaseyya na paritaseyya na bhāyeyya na santāsaṃ āpajjeyya, abhīrū assa achambhī anutrāsī apalāyī, pahīnabhayabheravo vigatalomahaṃso vihareyyāti – nindāya nappavedheyya. "
796915,149,2145,2,8,1,32,4,Na unnameyya pasaṃsito {bhikkhū}ti. 
796916,149,2145,9,79,1,507,66,"Idhekacce bhikkhū pasaṃsanti jātiyā vā gottena vā kolaputtiyena vā vaṇṇapokkharatāya vā dhanena vā ajjhenena vā kammāyatanena vā sippāyatanena vā vijjāṭṭhānena vā sutena vā paṭibhānena vā aññataraññatarena vā vatthunā pasaṃsanti thomenti kittenti vaṇṇenti, pasaṃsito thomito kittito vaṇṇito pasaṃsāya thomanena kittiyā vaṇṇahārikāya unnatiṃ na kareyya unnamaṃ na kareyya mānaṃ na kareyya thambhaṃ na kareyya, na tena mānaṃ janeyya na tena thaddho assa patthaddho paggahitasiroti– na unnameyya pasaṃsito bhikkhu. "
796917,149,2146,2,10,1,55,6,"Lobhaṃ saha macchariyena, kodhaṃ pesuṇiyañca {panudeyyā}ti. "
796918,149,2146,11,23,1,97,11,{Lobho}ti yo lobho lubbhanā lubbhitattaṃ sārāgo sārajjanā sārajjitattaṃ abhijjhā lobho akusalamūlaṃ. 
796919,149,2146,24,36,1,78,9,Macchariyan ti pañca macchariyāni– āvāsamacchariyaṃ… pe… gāho vuccati macchariyaṃ. 
796920,149,2146,37,77,1,279,31,"{Kodho}ti yo cittassa āghāto paṭighāto paṭighaṃ paṭivirodho, kopo pakopo sampakopo, doso padoso sampadoso, cittassa byāpatti manopadoso, kodho kujjhanā kujjhitattaṃ, doso dussanā dussitattaṃ, byāpattiṃ byāpajjanā byāpajjitattaṃ, virodho paṭivirodho caṇḍikkaṃ asuropo anattamanatā cittassa. "
796921,149,2146,78,97,1,123,18,"Pesuññan ti idhekacco pisuṇavāco hoti ito sutvā amutra akkhātā imesaṃ bhedāya, amutra vā sutvā imesaṃ akkhātā amūsaṃ bhedāya. "
796922,149,2146,98,118,1,133,17,"Iti samaggānaṃ vā bhettā bhinnānaṃ vā anuppadātā, vaggārāmo vaggarato vagganandī vaggakaraṇiṃ vācaṃ bhāsitā hoti– idaṃ vuccati pesuññaṃ. "
796923,149,2147,2,13,1,79,10,Api ca dvīhi kāraṇehi pesuññaṃ upasaṃharati– piyakamyatāya vā bhedādhippāyena vā. 
796924,149,2147,14,18,1,42,4,Kathaṃ piyakamyatāya pesuññaṃ upasaṃharati? 
796925,149,2147,19,30,1,107,11,Imassa piyo bhavissāmi manāpo bhavissāmi vissāsiko bhavissāmi abbhantariko bhavissāmi suhadayo bhavissāmīti. 
796926,149,2147,31,35,1,40,4,Evaṃ piyakamyatāya pesuññaṃ upasaṃharati. 
796927,149,2147,36,40,1,44,4,Kathaṃ bhedādhippāyena pesuññaṃ upasaṃharati? 
796928,149,2147,41,63,1,142,22,Kathaṃ ime nānā assu vinā assu vaggā assu dvedhā assu dvejjhā assu dve pakkhā assu bhijjheyyuṃ na samāgaccheyyuṃ dukkhaṃ na phāsu vihareyyunti. 
796929,149,2147,64,68,1,42,4,Evaṃ bhedādhippāyena pesuññaṃ upasaṃharati. 
796930,149,2147,69,77,1,55,6,"Lobhaṃ saha macchariyena, kodhaṃ pesuṇiyañca {panudeyyā}ti. "
796931,149,2147,78,98,1,170,18,"Lobhañca macchariyañca kodhañca pesuññañca nudeyya panudeyya pajaheyya vinodeyya byantiṃ kareyya anabhāvaṃ gameyyāti– lobhaṃ saha macchariyena, kodhaṃ pesuṇiyañca panudeyya. "
796932,149,2148,2,5,1,14,2,Tenāha bhagavā–
