796936,149,2152,2,11,1,60,8,"Kayavikkaye na tiṭṭheyya, upavādaṃ bhikkhu na kareyya kuhiñci; "
796937,149,2153,2,10,1,51,7,"Gāme ca nābhisajjeyya, lābhakamyā janaṃ na lapayeyya. "
796938,149,2154,2,8,1,26,3,Kayavikkaye na {tiṭṭheyyā}ti. 
796939,149,2154,9,18,1,63,9,Ye kayavikkayā vinaye paṭikkhittā na te imasmiṃ atthe adhippetā. 
796940,149,2154,19,22,1,27,3,Kathaṃ kayavikkaye tiṭṭhati? 
796941,149,2154,23,40,1,121,17,Pañcannaṃ saddhiṃ pattaṃ vā cīvaraṃ vā aññaṃ vā kiñci parikkhāraṃ vañcaniyaṃ vā karonto udayaṃ vā patthayanto parivatteti. 
796942,149,2154,41,44,1,25,3,Evaṃ kayavikkaye tiṭṭhati. 
796943,149,2154,45,49,1,30,4,Kathaṃ kayavikkaye na tiṭṭhati? 
796944,149,2154,50,69,1,127,19,Pañcannaṃ saddhiṃ pattaṃ vā cīvaraṃ vā aññaṃ vā kiñci parikkhāraṃ na vañcaniyaṃ vā karonto na udayaṃ vā patthayanto parivatteti. 
796945,149,2154,70,74,1,28,4,Evaṃ kayavikkaye na tiṭṭhati. 
796946,149,2154,75,79,1,26,3,Kayavikkaye na {tiṭṭheyyā}ti. 
796947,149,2154,80,110,1,249,27,"Kayavikkaye na tiṭṭheyya na santiṭṭheyya, kayavikkayaṃ pajaheyya vinodeyya byantiṃ kareyya anabhāvaṃ gameyya, kayavikkayā ārato assa virato paṭivirato nikkhanto nissaṭo vippamutto visaññutto vimariyādikatena cetasā vihareyyāti– kayavikkaye na tiṭṭheyya. "
796948,149,2155,2,8,1,37,5,Upavādaṃ bhikkhu na kareyya {kuhiñcī}ti. 
796949,149,2155,9,12,1,27,3,Katame upavādakarāti kilesā? 
796950,149,2155,13,46,1,265,29,"Santeke samaṇabrāhmaṇā iddhimanto dibbacakkhukā paracittaviduno, te dūratopi passanti āsannāpi na dissanti cetasāpi cittaṃ pajānanti, devatāpi kho santi iddhimantiniyo dibbacakkhukā paracittaviduniyo, tā dūratopi passanti, āsannāpi na dissanti cetasāpi cittaṃ pajānanti. "
796951,149,2155,47,58,1,81,11,Te oḷārikehi vā kilesehi majjhimehi vā kilesehi sukhumehi vā kilesehi upavadeyyuṃ. 
796952,149,2155,59,62,1,21,3,Katame oḷārikā kilesā? 
796953,149,2155,63,72,1,72,7,Kāyaduccaritaṃ vacīduccaritaṃ manoduccaritaṃ– ime vuccanti oḷārikā kilesā. 
796954,149,2155,73,76,1,22,3,Katame majjhimā kilesā? 
796955,149,2155,77,85,1,70,7,Kāmavitakko byāpādavitakko vihiṃsāvitakko– ime vuccanti majjhimā kilesā. 
796956,149,2155,86,89,1,21,3,Katame sukhumā kilesā? 
796957,149,2155,90,111,1,173,14,"Ñātivitakko, janapadavitakko, aparavitakko, parānudayatā paṭisaññutto vitakko , lābhasakkārasilokapaṭisaññutto vitakko, anavaññattipaṭisaññutto vitakko– ime vuccanti sukhumā kilesā. "
796958,149,2155,112,163,1,389,47,"Te oḷārikehi vā kilesehi majjhimehi vā kilesehi sukhumehi vā kilesehi na upavadeyya upavādaṃ na kareyya upavādakare kilese na kareyya na janeyya na sañjaneyya na nibbatteyya nābhinibbatteyya, upavādakare kilese pajaheyya vinodeyya byantiṃ kareyya anabhāvaṃ gameyya, upavādakarehi kilesehi ārato assa virato paṭivirato nikkhanto nissaṭo vippamutto visaññutto vimariyādikatena cetasā vihareyya. "
796959,149,2155,164,181,1,117,15,{Kuhiñcī}ti kuhiñci kimhici katthaci ajjhattaṃ vā bahiddhā vā ajjhattabahiddhā vāti– upavādaṃ bhikkhu na kareyya kuhiñci. 
796960,149,2156,2,6,1,23,3,Gāme ca {nābhisajjeyyā}ti. 
796961,149,2156,7,10,1,19,3,Kathaṃ gāme sajjati? 
796962,149,2156,11,29,1,150,17,"Idha bhikkhu gāme gihīhi saṃsaṭṭho viharati sahanandī sahasokī sukhitesu sukhito dukkhitesu dukkhito, uppannesu kiccakaraṇīyesu attanā voyogaṃ āpajjati. "
796963,149,2156,30,33,1,19,3,Evampi gāme sajjati. 
796964,149,2157,2,25,1,198,22,Atha vā bhikkhu pubbaṇhasamayaṃ nivāsetvā pattacīvaramādāya gāmaṃ vā nigamaṃ vā piṇḍāya pavisati arakkhiteneva kāyena arakkhitāya vācāya arakkhitena cittena anupaṭṭhitāya satiyā asaṃvutehi indriyehi. 
796965,149,2157,26,40,1,98,14,So tatra tatra sajjati tatra tatra gaṇhāti tatra tatra bajjhati tatra tatra anayabyasanaṃ āpajjati. 
796966,149,2157,41,44,1,19,3,Evampi gāme sajjati. 
796967,149,2158,2,6,1,22,4,Kathaṃ gāme na sajjati? 
796968,149,2158,7,30,1,166,22,"Idha bhikkhu gāme gihīhi asaṃsaṭṭho viharati na sahanandī na sahasokī na sukhitesu sukhito na dukkhitesu dukkhito, uppannesu kiccakaraṇīyesu na attanā voyogaṃ āpajjati. "
796969,149,2158,31,35,1,22,4,Evampi gāme na sajjati. 
796970,149,2159,2,24,1,192,22,Atha vā bhikkhu pubbaṇhasamayaṃ nivāsetvā pattacīvaramādāya gāmaṃ vā nigamaṃ vā piṇḍāya pavisati rakkhiteneva kāyena rakkhitāya vācāya rakkhitena cittena upaṭṭhitāya satiyā saṃvutehi indriyehi. 
796971,149,2159,25,43,1,110,18,So tatra tatra na sajjati tatra tatra na gaṇhāti tatra tatra na bajjhati tatra tatra na anayabyasanaṃ āpajjati. 
796972,149,2159,44,48,1,22,4,Evampi gāme na sajjati. 
796973,149,2159,49,82,1,218,27,"Gāme ca {nābhisajjeyyā}ti gāme na sajjeyya na gaṇheyya na bajjheyya na palibajjheyya, agiddho assa agadhito amucchito anajjhosanno vītagedho vigatagedho cattagedho… pe… brahmabhūtena attanā vihareyyāti– gāme ca nābhisajjeyya. "
796974,149,2160,2,7,1,31,4,Lābhakamyā janaṃ na {lapayeyyā}ti. 
796975,149,2160,8,10,1,13,2,Katamā lapanā? 
796976,149,2160,11,71,1,353,30,"Lābhasakkārasilokasannissitassa pāpicchassa icchāpakatassa āmisacakkhukassa lokadhammagarukassa yā paresaṃ ālapanā lapanā sallapanā ullapanā samullapanā unnahanā samunnahanā ukkācanā samukkācanā[ ukkāpanā samukkāpanā( syā.)] anupiyabhāṇitā cātukamyatā muggasūpyatā pāribhaṭayatā parapiṭṭhimaṃsikatā[ piṭṭhimaṃsikatā( ka.) visuddhimagge sīlaniddesavaṇṇanā oloketabbā], yā tattha saṇhavācatā sakhilavācatā sithilavācatā[ mettavācakatā( syā.)] apharusavācatā– ayaṃ vuccati lapanā. "
796977,149,2161,2,28,1,154,24,"Api ca dvīhi kāraṇehi janaṃ lapati– attānaṃ vā nīcaṃ ṭhapento paraṃ uccaṃ ṭhapento janaṃ lapati, attānaṃ vā uccaṃ ṭhapento paraṃ nīcaṃ ṭhapento janaṃ lapati. "
796978,149,2161,29,38,1,63,9,Kathaṃ attānaṃ nīcaṃ ṭhapento paraṃ uccaṃ ṭhapento janaṃ lapati?
796979,149,2161,39,72,1,237,28,"‘‘ Tumhe me bahūpakārā, ahaṃ tumhe nissāya labhāmi cīvarapiṇḍapātasenāsanagilānapaccayabhesajjaparikkhāraṃ, yepi me aññe dātuṃ vā kātuṃ vā maññanti, tumhe nissāya tumhe sampassantā yampi me purāṇaṃ mātāpettikaṃ nāmadheyyaṃ tampi me antarahitaṃ. "
796980,149,2161,73,83,1,57,8,Tumhehi ahaṃ ñāyāmi asukassa kulūpako asukāya kulūpako’’ ti. 
796981,149,2161,84,93,1,61,9,Evaṃ attānaṃ nīcaṃ ṭhapento paraṃ uccaṃ ṭhapento janaṃ lapati. 
796982,149,2162,2,11,1,63,9,Kathaṃ attānaṃ uccaṃ ṭhapento paraṃ nīcaṃ ṭhapento janaṃ lapati?
796983,149,2162,12,47,1,236,25,"‘‘ Ahaṃ tumhākaṃ bahūpakāro, tumhe maṃ āgamma buddhaṃ saraṇaṃ gatā, dhammaṃ saraṇaṃ gatā, saṅghaṃ saraṇaṃ gatā, pāṇātipātā paṭiviratā, adinnādānā paṭiviratā, kāmesumicchācārā paṭiviratā, musāvādā paṭiviratā, surāmerayamajjappamādaṭṭhānā paṭiviratā. "
796984,149,2162,48,61,1,85,10,"Ahaṃ tumhākaṃ uddesaṃ demi, paripucchaṃ demi, uposathaṃ ācikkhāmi, navakammaṃ adhiṭṭhāmi. "
796985,149,2162,62,76,1,77,12,Atha pana tumhe maṃ ujjhitvā aññe sakkarotha garuṃ karotha mānetha pūjethā’’ ti. 
796986,149,2162,77,87,1,61,9,Evaṃ attānaṃ uccaṃ ṭhapento paraṃ nīcaṃ ṭhapento janaṃ lapati. 
796987,149,2163,2,9,1,31,4,Lābhakamyā janaṃ na {lapayeyyā}ti. 
796988,149,2163,10,45,1,295,32,"Lābhahetu lābhapaccayā lābhakāraṇā lābhābhinibbattiyā lābhaṃ paripācento janaṃ na lapayeyya, lapanaṃ pajaheyya vinodeyya byantiṃ kareyya anabhāvaṃ gameyya, lapanā ārato assa virato paṭivirato nikkhanto nissaṭo vippamutto visaññutto vimariyādikatena cetasā vihareyyāti– lābhakamyā janaṃ na lapayeyya. "
