797022,149,2177,8,36,1,212,22,"Idhekacco jantāghare acittīkārakato there bhikkhū ghaṭṭayantopi tiṭṭhati, ghaṭṭayantopi nisīdati, puratopi tiṭṭhati, puratopi nisīdati, uccepi āsane nisīdati, anāpucchāpi kaṭṭhaṃ pakkhipati, anāpucchāpi dvāraṃ pidahati. "
797023,149,2177,37,42,1,43,5,Evaṃ jantāghare kāyikaṃ pāgabbhiyaṃ dasseti. 
797024,149,2178,2,7,1,46,5,Kathaṃ udakatitthe kāyikaṃ pāgabbhiyaṃ dasseti? 
