797054,149,2185,20,37,1,66,11,‘‘ na tvaṃ imaṃ dhammavinayaṃ ājānāsi… pe… nibbeṭhehi vā sace pahosī’’ ti. 
797055,149,2185,38,40,1,21,2,Vuttañhetaṃ bhagavatā–
797056,149,2185,41,68,1,150,17,"‘‘ viggāhikāya kho, moggallāna, kathāya sati kathābāhullaṃ pāṭikaṅkhaṃ, kathābāhulle sati uddhaccaṃ, uddhatassa asaṃvaro, asaṃvutassa ārā cittaṃ samādhimhā’’ ti. "
797057,149,2185,69,74,1,33,4,Kathaṃ viggāhikaṃ na {kathayeyyā}ti. 
797058,149,2185,75,112,1,291,34,"Viggāhikaṃ kathaṃ na katheyya na bhaṇeyya na dīpeyya na vohareyya, viggāhikaṃ kathaṃ pajaheyya vinodeyya byantiṃ kareyya anabhāvaṃ gameyya, viggāhikakathāya ārato assa virato paṭivirato nikkhanto nissaṭo vippamutto visaññutto vimariyādikatena cetasā vihareyyāti– kathaṃ viggāhikaṃ na kathayeyya. "
