797076,149,2193,36,77,1,299,35,"Sampajāno hutvā sāṭheyyaṃ na kareyya na janeyya na sañjaneyya na nibbatteyya nābhinibbatteyya, sāṭheyyaṃ pajaheyya vinodeyya byantiṃ kareyya anabhāvaṃ gameyya, sāṭheyyā ārato assa virato paṭivirato nikkhanto nissaṭo vippamutto visaññutto vimariyādikatena cetasā vihareyyāti– sampajāno saṭhāni na kayirā. "
797077,149,2194,2,9,1,50,5,"Atha jīvitena paññāya, sīlabbatena {nāññamatimaññe}ti. "
