798419,149,2733,22,30,1,63,8,Sayanaṃ vuccati senāsanaṃ vihāro aḍḍhayogo pāsādo hammiyaṃ guhā. 
798420,149,2733,31,48,1,147,14,"Taṃ sayanāsanaṃ asappāyarūpadassanena rittaṃ vivittaṃ pavivittaṃ, asappāyasaddassavanena… pe… asappāyehi pañcahi kāmaguṇehi rittaṃ vivittaṃ pavivittaṃ. "
