798439,149,2744,2,8,1,35,5,Pañcannaṃ dhīro bhayānaṃ na {bhāye}ti. 
798440,149,2744,9,18,1,59,8,{Dhīro}ti dhīro paṇḍito paññavā buddhimā ñāṇī vibhāvī medhāvī. 
798441,149,2744,19,51,1,232,29,"Dhīro pañcannaṃ bhayānaṃ na bhāyeyya na taseyya na santaseyya na uttaseyya na parittaseyya na santāsaṃ āpajjeyya , abhīrū assa acchambhī anutrāsī apalāyī pahīnabhayabheravo vigatalomahaṃso vihareyyāti– pañcannaṃ dhīro bhayānaṃ na bhāye. "
798442,149,2745,2,6,1,30,3,Bhikkhu sato {sapariyantacārī}ti. 
798443,149,2745,7,15,1,58,7,{Bhikkhū}ti puthujjanakalyāṇako vā bhikkhu sekkho vā bhikkhu. 
798444,149,2745,16,41,1,159,18,"{Sato}ti catūhi kāraṇehi sato– kāye kāyānupassanāsatipaṭṭhānaṃ bhāvento sato, vedanāsu… pe… citte… dhammesu dhammānupassanāsatipaṭṭhānaṃ bhāvento sato– so vuccati sato. "
798445,149,2745,42,55,1,132,8,"{Sapariyantacārī}ti cattāro pariyantā– sīlasaṃvarapariyanto, indriyasaṃvarapariyanto, bhojane mattaññutāpariyanto, jāgariyānuyogapariyanto. "
798446,149,2746,2,5,1,27,2,Katamo sīlasaṃvarapariyanto? 
798447,149,2746,6,23,1,141,13,"Idha bhikkhu sīlavā hoti, pātimokkhasaṃvarasaṃvuto viharati ācāragocarasampanno, aṇumattesu vajjesu bhayadassāvī, samādāya sikkhati sikkhāpadesu . "
798448,149,2746,24,36,1,111,10,"Antopūtibhāvaṃ paccavekkhamāno anto sīlasaṃvarapariyante carati, mariyādaṃ na bhindati– ayaṃ sīlasaṃvarapariyanto. "
798449,149,2747,2,4,1,30,2,Katamo indriyasaṃvarapariyanto? 
798450,149,2747,5,14,1,72,9,Idha bhikkhu cakkhunā rūpaṃ disvā na nimittaggāhī hoti nānubyañjanaggāhī. 
798451,149,2747,15,23,1,53,5,Yatvādhikaraṇamenaṃ… pe… cakkhundriye saṃvaraṃ āpajjati. 
798452,149,2747,24,47,1,156,19,Sotena saddaṃ sutvā… ghānena gandhaṃ ghāyitvā… jivhāya rasaṃ sāyitvā… kāyena phoṭṭhabbaṃ phusitvā… manasā dhammaṃ viññāya na nimittaggāhī hoti nānubyañjanaggāhī. 
798453,149,2747,48,68,1,186,17,"Yatvādhikaraṇamenaṃ manindriyaṃ susaṃvutaṃ viharantaṃ abhijjhādomanassā pāpakā akusalā dhammā nānvāssaveyyuṃ, tassa saṃvarāya paṭipajjati, rakkhati manindriyaṃ, manindriye saṃvaraṃ āpajjati. "
798454,149,2747,69,81,1,118,10,"Ādittapariyāyaṃ paccavekkhamāno anto indriyasaṃvarapariyante carati, mariyādaṃ na bhindati– ayaṃ indriyasaṃvarapariyanto. "
798455,149,2748,2,5,1,34,3,Katamo bhojane mattaññutāpariyanto? 
798456,149,2748,6,30,1,174,21,"Idha bhikkhu paṭisaṅkhā yoniso āhāraṃ āhāreti neva davāya na madāya na maṇḍanāya na vibhūsanāya, yāvadeva imassa kāyassa ṭhitiyā yāpanāya vihiṃsūparatiyā brahmacariyānuggahāya. "
798457,149,2748,31,48,1,119,16,"Iti purāṇañca vedanaṃ paṭihaṅkhāmi navañca vedanaṃ na uppādessāmi, yātrā ca me bhavissati anavajjatā ca phāsuvihāro cāti. "
798458,149,2748,49,63,1,156,12,"Akkhabbhañjanavaṇapaṭicchādanaputtamaṃsūpamaṃ paccavekkhamāno anto bhojane mattaññutāpariyante carati, mariyādaṃ na bhindati– ayaṃ bhojane mattaññutāpariyanto. "
798459,149,2749,2,4,1,30,2,Katamo jāgariyānuyogapariyanto? 
798460,149,2749,5,51,1,386,43,"Idha bhikkhu divasaṃ caṅkamena nisajjāya āvaraṇīyehi dhammehi cittaṃ parisodheti, rattiyā paṭhamaṃ yāmaṃ caṅkamena nisajjāya āvaraṇīyehi dhammehi cittaṃ parisodheti, rattiyā majjhimaṃ yāmaṃ dakkhiṇena passena sīhaseyyaṃ kappeti pāde pādaṃ accādhāya sato sampajāno uṭṭhānasaññaṃ manasi karitvā, rattiyā pacchimaṃ yāmaṃ paccuṭṭhāya caṅkamena nisajjāya āvaraṇīyehi dhammehi cittaṃ parisodheti. "
798461,149,2749,52,77,1,154,13,"Bhaddekarattavihāraṃ[ bhaddekarattivihāraṃ( sī. ka.)] paccavekkhamāno anto jāgariyānuyogapariyante carati, mariyādaṃ na bhindati– ayaṃ jāgariyānuyogapariyantoti– bhikkhu sato sapariyantacārī. "
798462,149,2750,2,5,1,30,3,Ḍaṃsādhipātānaṃ sarīsapānan ti. 
