798494,149,2764,2,18,1,59,6,"Ātaṅkaphassena khudāya phuṭṭho, sītaṃ athuṇhaṃ[ atuṇhaṃ( sī. ka.)] adhivāsayeyya; "
798495,149,2765,2,11,1,61,8,"So tehi phuṭṭho bahudhā anoko, vīriyaparakkamaṃ daḷhaṃ kareyya. "
798496,149,2766,2,6,1,32,3,Ātaṅkaphassena khudāya {phuṭṭho}ti. 
798497,149,2766,7,10,1,31,3,Ātaṅkaphasso vuccati rogaphasso. 
798498,149,2766,11,17,1,53,6,Rogaphassena phuṭṭho pareto samohito samannāgato assa; 
798499,149,2766,18,41,1,182,17,"cakkhurogena phuṭṭho pareto samohito samannāgato assa, sotarogena… ghānarogena… jivhārogena… kāyarogena… pe… ḍaṃsamakasavātātapasarīsapasamphassena phuṭṭho pareto samohito samannāgato assa. "
798500,149,2766,42,45,1,21,3,Khudā vuccati chātako. 
798501,149,2766,46,56,1,83,9,Chātakena phuṭṭho pareto samohito samannāgato assāti– ātaṅkaphassena khudāya phuṭṭho. 
798502,149,2767,2,6,1,30,3,Sītaṃ athuṇhaṃ {adhivāsayeyyā}ti. 
798503,149,2767,7,31,1,110,15,"Sītan ti dvīhi kāraṇehi sītaṃ hoti– abbhantaradhātuppakopavasena[ abbhantaradhātusaṅkopavasena( syā.)] vā sītaṃ hoti, bahiddhā utuvasena vā sītaṃ hoti. "
798504,149,2767,32,53,1,127,17,"Uṇhan ti dvīhi kāraṇehi uṇhaṃ hoti– abbhantaradhātuppakopavasena vā uṇhaṃ hoti, bahiddhā utuvasena vā uṇhaṃ hotīti– sītaṃ athuṇhaṃ . "
798505,149,2767,54,93,1,297,26,{Adhivāsayeyyā}ti khamo assa sītassa uṇhassa jighacchāya pipāsāya ḍaṃsamakasavātātapasarīsapasamphassānaṃ duruttānaṃ durāgatānaṃ vacanapathānaṃ uppannānaṃ sārīrikānaṃ vedanānaṃ dukkhānaṃ tibbānaṃ[ tippānaṃ( sī. syā.)] kharānaṃ kaṭukānaṃ asātānaṃ amanāpānaṃ pāṇaharānaṃ adhivāsakajātiko assāti– sītaṃ athuṇhaṃ adhivāsayeyya. 
798506,149,2768,2,8,1,31,5,So tehi phuṭṭho bahudhā {anoko}ti. 
798507,149,2768,9,29,1,117,18,So {tehī}ti ātaṅkaphassena ca khudāya ca sītena ca uṇhena ca phuṭṭho pareto samohito samannāgato assāti– so tehi phuṭṭho. 
798508,149,2768,30,45,1,97,12,{Bahudhā}ti anekavidhehi ākārehi phuṭṭho pareto samohito samannāgato assāti– so tehi phuṭṭho bahudhā . 
798509,149,2768,46,54,1,65,6,{Anoko}ti abhisaṅkhārasahagataviññāṇassa okāsaṃ na karotītipi– anoko. 
798510,149,2768,55,71,1,117,14,Atha vā kāyaduccaritassa vacīduccaritassa manoduccaritassa okāsaṃ na karotītipi– anokoti– so tehi phuṭṭho bahudhā anoko. 
798511,149,2769,2,6,1,33,3,Vīriyaparakkamaṃ daḷhaṃ {kareyyā}ti. 
798512,149,2769,7,29,1,238,22,Vīriyaparakkamo vuccati yo cetasiko vīriyārambho nikkamo parakkamo uyyāmo vāyāmo ussāho ussoḷhī appaṭivānī thāmo dhiti asithilaparakkamatā anikkhittacchandatā anikkhittadhuratā dhurasampaggāho vīriyaṃ vīriyindriyaṃ vīriyabalaṃ sammāvāyāmo. 
798513,149,2769,30,34,1,33,3,Vīriyaparakkamaṃ daḷhaṃ {kareyyā}ti. 
798514,149,2769,35,49,1,119,12,"Vīriyaṃ parakkamaṃ daḷhaṃ kareyya thiraṃ kareyya, daḷhasamādāno assa avatthitasamādānoti– vīriyaparakkamaṃ daḷhaṃ kareyya. "
