798720,149,2851,29,32,1,20,3,Evampi pādalolo hoti. 
798721,149,2852,2,22,1,153,18,"Atha vā bhikkhu antopi saṅghārāme pādalolo pādaloliyena samannāgato hoti, na atthahetu na kāraṇahetu uddhato avūpasantacitto pariveṇato pariveṇaṃ gacchati. "
